A prominent, bright blue glass chandelier hangs from the ceiling. In the corner, there is a curved grey velvet sofa with several throw pillows. The floor is covered in a light-colored rug with a blue grid pattern. To the left, a blue reflective table surface is visible, and a doorway leads to another room. To the right, another doorway is open, showing a glimpse into an adjacent room with similar flooring.
